_sText:
This was my first map I ever made, although I stopped fixing it until now.

It contains 60 CT spawns and 2 T spawns, 17 - 21 Traps.
- Breakable floors/glass
- Fans
- Crushers
- Lasers
- Spinning Plate
- Explosions
- Etc.

I tested it with my friend Chicken McFail and his server, he made and using hamachi to connect the Ips.
This is still Beta and I would like some comments that will improve my map for the future.

Updated.
Changed the textures to combine, also increased the height of the map and changed a couple of traps.

I've made an version 2 of this map, although I reformatted and this map got lost so I gave up on it...
